      authorbio:
        "In addition to her first three books about the Willow family, <i>Hamster Magic,</i> <i>Lawn Mower Magic, </i>and <i>Grasshopper Magic, </i>LYNNE JONELL is the author of the popular<i> Emmy and the Incredible Shrinking Rat,</i> a Booklist Editor's Choice, and one of School Library Journal's Best Books of the Year.&#160; She has also written three other novels and seven picture books.&#160; She has never eaten a grasshopper, but that's only because she hasn't found a magic one yet.<br><br>BRANDON DORMAN has created hundreds of illustrations for books and magazines, including the cover art for the Newbery Honor Book <i>Savvy. </i>He loves string cheese and sunflower seeds, and once licked a slug. He lives in Puyallup, Washington, with his wife and two rambunctious sons.",
