      authorbio:
        "LANIE BROSS is the author of <i>Fates,</i> and, as Lee Bross, <i>Tangled Webs</i>. She was born in a small town in Maine, where she spent the next eighteen years dreaming of bigger places. After exploring city life, she and her husband and two young sons ended up going right back to the wilds of Maine. They now live just one house down from where she grew up. Fate, perhaps? Lanie loves chasing her rambunctious kids, playing tug-of-war with her ninety-five-pound Lab, and writing for teens. Visit her online at leebross.com and follow her on Tumblr and Twitter.",
